post_text:
TONIGHT:
Monday, June 9 -- 7:30pm
Union High School Football Stadium
The Union Boosters will be holding an event on Monday June 9th - to help increase our student participation in the upcoming fall sports/activities. This includes our high school and junior high football programs.
We are looking for community support to help create excitement to get our students excited to participate in our upcoming fall sports/activities.
All parents, student athletes, community members are urged to attend.
